ium phosphate-sodium phosphate)." Patrin Pharma, Skokie, IL.[5] "Product Information. SSKI (potassium iodide)." Upsher-Smith Laboratories Inc, Minneapolis, MN.[6] "Product Information. Potassium Chloride (potassium chloride)." Pharmaceutical Assoc Inc Div Beach Products, Greenville, SC.', 1767363027);
